hero.description: I'm a developer specialized in creating web applications, you will find in this portfolio my skills and personal projects.

projects.title: Projects
projects.lesmots: "Les Mots" is a game where the goal is to find all the french words with 9 given random letters.
projects.aest: "Aest" is a game attempting to reproduce a training tool for visual assessment of crop diseases.
projects.toutcourt: "Tout court" repoduces a simple tennis courts booking system. This project was built in 3 days for the end of my web developer training.
